The settings is below,  vscode can open the Hyper app, but lose the current location. It always use the home location. 
```js
// Place your settings in this file to overwrite the default settings
{
	"terminal.external.windowsExec": "C:\\Users\\bang\\AppData\\Local\\hyper\\app-1.0.0\\Hyper.exe",
	"npm.runInTerminal": false
}
```
